    init                initialize a native PE project
    inspect-pe          parse PE32 or PE32+ metadata
    pdb-inspect         inspect an MSF 7.0 PDB and optionally match it to a PE
    diff-function       compare a linked PE function to a COFF symbol
    lib-inspect         inspect a COFF archive/static or import library
    coff-comdat-resolve
                        resolve COMDAT groups across COFF objects
    map-inspect         parse an MSVC-compatible linker map
    layout-reconstruct  correlate PE sections, linker map contributions, and
                        COFF objects
    image-profile       derive a target-specific whole-image profile
    image-match         compare complete PE images under an explicit layout
                        profile
    metadata-scan       recover bounded MSVC RTTI, vtables, unwind, TLS, and
                        initializer metadata
    corpus-create-manifest
                        create the bundled compiler ground-truth manifest
    corpus-build        build a reproducible compiler/version ground-truth
                        corpus
    corpus-verify       verify source and output hashes in a ground-truth
                        corpus
    corpus-compare      compare compiler/version ground-truth corpus reports
    corpus-generate     generate a deterministic parameterized C/C++ source
                        corpus
    corpus-generated-verify
                        verify generated corpus source identities
    test-bundle-create  create a hash-sealed authorized static test bundle
    test-bundle-inspect
                        safely extract, verify, and statically inspect an
                        authorized test bundle
    symbolic-memory-validate
                        angr comparison with symbolic region bases and alias
                        constraints
    hybrid-generate     compatibility alias for: x86decomp hybrid generate
    target-pack-infer   infer a fact-preserving target pack and template plan
    template-derive     derive a grounded project-template contract from a
                        target pack
    template-materialize
